--- @target: std.json
JSON parsing and serialization for map text-to-text structures.
---

--- @target: parse
Parses a JSON string into a map of text keys to text values.

@param input A JSON-formatted text string.
@return A result containing the parsed @link map, or an error if parsing fails.
---

--- @target: stringify
Serializes a map of text keys to text values into a compact JSON string.

@param value The map to serialize.
@return A JSON text string representation.
---

--- @target: pretty
Serializes a map of text keys to text values into a pretty-printed JSON string with indentation.

@param value The map to serialize.
@param indent Number of spaces per indentation level. Defaults to 2.
@return A formatted JSON text string with indentation and line breaks.
---
